creator: Oakridge International School
descriptionHtml:
The Oakridge International School App is an easy to use application which makes interacting with the school a breeze. By downloading this app, parents would have a bouquet of services at their fingertips. The app would serve as the one place for all student related information and application.

Parents can avail the following services on the app:

Fee Payment
Leave Application
Helpdesk
Student Attendance
School Notification
Update profile

Download the app now and be in control of your child’s education.
descriptionShort: Use this app to pay school fees, apply for leave, receive notifications and more
